ChartDataValue = object
  case kind*: ChartDataValueType
  of INTEGER_VALUE:
      ival*: int

  of FLOAT_VALUE:
      fval*: float

  of STRING_VALUE:
      sval*: string

  of CHAR_VALUE:
      cval*: char

  
ChartData = ref object
  chart_type*: ChartType
  data_color*: ColorRef
  data_name*: string
  x_axis*: seq[ChartDataValue]
  y_axis*: seq[ChartDataValue]
